                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="dialog-formal-situation-neutral-situation-dan-informal-situation-beserta-gambar-nya">
                            9. dialog formal situation, neutral situation, dan informal situation beserta gambar nya</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jadi gini :</strong></p><p>formal
</p><p>A: "Excuse me, may I enter?"
</p><p>B: "Sure, you may. Is there anything that I can help?"
</p><p>A: "Yes. My apologize, but I couldn't finish the report on time."
</p><p>B: "It doesn't matter."
</p><p>
</p><p>informal
</p><p>A: "Yo, Josh! What's up?"
</p><p>B: "Nothing. You?"
</p><p>A: "Nothing. I'm just pissed at our teacher."
</p><p>B: "You're always pissed at everyone.
</p><p>
</p><p>neutral/normal
</p><p>A: "Good morning, how are you doing?"
</p><p>B: "I'm fine. You?"
</p><p>A: "I'm also fine. Thank you for asking."
</p><p>B: "No problem."</p><br />
