                            26. dikerjakan situation 2 sampai 5​</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p><strong>Situation 2.</strong></p><p>Ali : <strong>Good bye</strong>, mam.</p><p>Teacher : <strong>Good bye, </strong>Ali. Take care on the way and see you.</p><p>Ali : Thanks, mam and <strong>see you</strong> next time Insyah Allah.</p><p></p><p><strong>Situation 3.</strong></p><p>Ahmad : <strong>Good night, </strong>dad,</p><p>Dad : <strong>Good night too</strong>, honey. Have a nice dream.</p><p>Ahmad : <strong>Have a nice dream, </strong>too dad.</p><p></p><p><strong>Situation 4.</strong></p><p>Zainab : May I borrow your pen, Ummu?</p><p>Ummu : Sure, here it is. / Sure, which one do you want?</p><p>Zainab : Thank a lot, Ummu.</p><p>Ummu : You are welcome, Zainab.</p><p></p><p><strong>Situation 5.</strong></p><p>You : Assalamualaikum, <strong>I am sorry,</strong> mam I'm late.</p><p>Teacher : Why are you late?</p><p>You : <strong>I'm late</strong> because I over sleep, mam.</p><p>Teacher : Okay other time you don't come late again!.</p><p>You : Okay, mam. Thank you.</p><p></p><p><strong>Penjelasan:</strong></p><p><strong>Situation 1 </strong>sampai <strong>situation 5</strong> meminta kita untuk mengisi dialog yang rumpang, menjadi lengkap dan sempurna.</p><p></p><p>jadikan jawaban terbaik jika membantu ya!</p><br />
