                            30. situation 5 dan 6 ya :) makasih yg udh mau ngejawab</h2><br />
                        udin: that sounds healthy<br />lina; yes i agree and lets live a healthy life<br /><br />udin; i heard that too. what do you think, lina?<br />lina; i agree, lets visit our teacher and bring something for him as our appreciation <br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="5-the-situation-in-the-market-is-very-%e2%80%8b">
                            31. 5. The situation in the market is very ....​</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>The situation in the market is very crowded</p><p><strong>Penjelasan:</strong></p><p>Crowded = Ramai</p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="buatlah-compliments-arau-caresympathy-dari-situasi-berikut-beserta-responnyaa-complimentssituation-1you-see-your-friend-her-new-haircut-situation-2you-sister-can-drive-very-wellsituation-3yo">
                            32. Buatlah compliments arau care/sympathy dari situasi berikut beserta responnya!
A. COMPLIMENTS
Situation 1
You see your friend her new haircut.
Situation 2
You sister can drive very well
Situation 3
Your best friend handled the problem successfully.
Situation 4
You visit your friend's house for the first time.
Situation 5
You friend submitted her project on time.
Situation 6
Your sister's team won a game
Situation 7
Your brother has just bought a new, smart robot
Situation 8
Your friend has a new T-shirt.
B. CARE/SYMPATHY
situation 1
Your friend has just lost his jacket.
Situation 2
Your brother is sick
Situation 3
Your younger sister got a bad score
Situation 4
Your friend did not win the drawing competition 
Situation 5
Your friend's father has just lost his company.
Situation 6
Your friend's grandmother has passed away
Situation 7
Your friend has just got an accident
Situation 8
Your friend got his motorbike stolen.</h2><br />
                        S.1<br />What a cute new haircut!<br /><br />S.2<br />You look so enjoy in drive, You must be practice well.<br /><br />S.3<br />Congratulation! you're a good fixer<br /><br />S.4<br />How cozy your house!<br /><br />S.5<br />Excellent! You're so discipline<br /><br />S.6<br />Awesome! you really do the best !<br /><br />S.7<br />Incredible robot! where did you buy it?<br /><br />S.8<br />I like your t-shirt, it's a beautiful t-shirt!<br /><br /><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="number-55-match-the-situation-with-the-appropriate-notice%e2%80%8b">
                            33. number 55. Match the situation with the appropriate notice!​</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>5. cocokkan situasi dengan pemberitahuan yang sesuai!</p><p>~penerjemahnya</p><p><strong>Penjelasan:</strong></p><p>biasanya isi nya ada di dalam teks jadi saya hanya menerjemahkannya saja</p><p>semoga membantu</p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="situation-6-your-younger-sister-got-a-bad-score-buatlah-5-expression-showing-care-dari-situation-tersebut-tolong-dibantu">
                            34. Situation 6: your younger sister got a bad score.  buatlah 5 expression showing care dari situation tersebut..  tolong dibantu..  </h2><br />
                        Situasi ke 6 : Adik kecil mu mendapat nilai buruk.<br />Ekspresi mu sperti apa? Klau aku membantu dia jika dia membutuhkan bantuan, klau tidak biarkan :v  <br /><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="tolong-dijawab-yg-situation-2-dan-situation-3%e2%80%8b">
                            35.  tolong dijawab yg situation 2 dan situation 3​</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>sit 2 : i hope you will win</p><p></p><p>sit 3 : nice</p><p></p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="tolong-bantuannya-situation-2-5">
                            36. Tolong bantuannya:)   ( Situation 2 - 5 ).</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>2. Wow, it's beautiful. I'm sure she will like your drawing.</p><p></p><p>3. It looks so nice. I'm sure everybody will love it.</p><p></p><p>4. You're good, Beni. Thank you so much.</p><p></p><p>5. Fabulous! You sing like a real singer! You will definitely get a big applause for that!</p><p></p><p>2.I love your drawing. I'm certain she will like it</p><p>3.it looks delicious. I'm sure everybody will like it.</p><p>4.the floor is really clean, good job. Thank you for that</p><p>5. you sound just like a real singer. I know you'll get a big applause for that.</p><p></p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="bahasa-inggrisyang-situation-4-and-5">
                            37. bahasa inggrisyang situation 4 and 5</h2><br />
                        <p><strong> 4. I‘m happy to hear that. I hope that you can be accepted by the company.</strong></p><p><strong>5.That’s terrible! I hope that it doesn’t cause huge destruction.</strong></p><p></p>Pembahasan<p>Ada dua ungkapan (expression) yang digunakan dalam soal ini, yaitu expression of happines and sympathy, dan expression of hope.</p><p></p><strong>Expression of happiness and sadness</strong><p>Expression of happiness and sympathy adalah ungkapan yang digunakan untuk menyatakan perasaan senang/bahagia dan mengungkapkan rasa simpati. Beberapa ungkapan yang sering digunakan antara lain:</p><p><strong>Happiness: </strong></p>I am happy to hear that. It was great!It gives me great pleasure!Fantastic!Great!It’s so exciting!<p></p><p><strong>Sympathy:</strong></p>You must be very upset about it.I am sorry to hear that!I hope things get better soon.What a pity.That’s terrible!That’s so sad.<p></p><p>Expression of hope</p><p>Untuk mengungkapkan harapan, umumnya menggunakan kata hope. Ada dua cara penggunaan kata hope, yaitu</p><strong>hope + (that) + clause</strong><p>I hope (that) you can make your dream come true.</p><p>I hope (that) you can pass the test and get good grades.</p><p>That boleh digunakan, boleh juga tidak digunakan.</p><p></p><strong>hope + to infinitive/be</strong><p>I hope to be the best student.</p><p>I hope to sleep well tonight.</p><p></p><p>***</p><p>4. Your brother is going to have a job interview. You are happy for him and hope he will be accepted by the company. ~ Saudara laki-laki mu akan menghadapi wawancara kerja. Kamu sangat senang dan berharap dia dapat diterima di perusahaan tersebut.</p><p></p><p>The conversation:</p><p>Your brother: I am going to attend a job interview. Please pray for me.</p><p>You: <strong> I‘m happy to hear that. I hope that you can be accepted by the company.</strong></p><p></p><p>5. Your sister told you a landslide occurred in your uncle’s village.You feel sad and hope it doesn’t cause huge destruction. ~ Saudara perempuanmu memberitahukan bahwa telah terjadi longsor di desa pamanmu. Kamu merasa sedih dan berharap tidak terjadi kerusakan yang besar.</p><p></p><p>The conversation:</p><p>Your sister: You know what! A landslide occurred in our uncle’s village.</p><p>You: <strong>That’s terrible! I hope that it doesn’t cause huge destruction.</strong></p><p></p>Pelajari lebih lanjut:<p><strong>Mengenai expression of hope:</strong></p>https://brainly.co.id/tugas/1139218https://brainly.co.id/tugas/42105047https://brainly.co.id/tugas/40065053<p>_______________________________________________</p>DETAIL JAWABAN<p><strong>Kelas: </strong>8</p><p><strong>Mapel:</strong> Bahasa Inggris</p><p><strong>Materi:</strong> Expression of hope</p><p><strong>Kode:</strong> 8.5.x</p><p><strong></strong></p><p><strong>#SolusiBrainlyCommunity</strong></p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="tolong-di-terjemahkan-situation-2-sampai-situation-9">
                            38. tolong di terjemahkan. situation 2 sampai situation 9</h2><br />
                        <p>situation 7=Beni:udin, kamu terlihat kesal. apa yang terjadi?</p><p>Udin:aku sangat kecewa dengan kualitas ponsel yang aku beli. ini tidak sebagus yang ada di iklan.</p><p>Edo:saya turut menyesal</p><p></p><p>situation 8=siti:aku sangat marah</p><p>Dayu:apa yang terjadi?</p><p>Siti:Nita berbuat curang selama test tetapi dia mendapat nilai lebih bagus dari aku</p><p>Dayu:ini jelek sekali. bersabarlah. bersikap marah tidak akan merubah apapun</p><p></p><p>situation 9=Beni:apakah kamu tau Maharani?</p><p>Siti:ya aku tau</p><p>Beni:bagaimana dia?</p><p>siti:dia sangat baik dan sopan.dia juga sangat pandai</p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="situation-5siti-i-need-some-chickenudinlina">
                            39. Situation 5
Siti: "I need some chicken"
Udin:
Lina:</h2><br />
                        Judul babnya apa? Apa pokok bahasannya ?Siti : " I need some chicken. "<br />Udin : " Hm... I'm sorry, Siti. I don't have it. I can't help you. Are you have it, Lina? "<br />Lina : " Some chicken? Oh, I think I have it. I can give you some, Siti. Don't worry about that. "<br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="bantu-jwb-plsss-situation-1-5-bsk-dikumpul">
                            40. bantu jwb plsss situation 1-5 bsk dikumpul</h2><br />
                        <p>1. congratulations! please be careful there and don't forget to text me your experience when you're not busy</p><p>2. that was awesome! don't be sad because you are a runner up, you should be proud of it. i believe one day you will actually win it.</p><p>3. congratulations, dad! i'm proud of you and i always know you can do it</p><p>4. that is awesome! thank you so much, brother, it means a lot to me</p><p>5. wow, that's incredible! believe me, i would like to have 3 houses like this </p><br />
                    
